## ⚙️ STM32CubeMX Configuration (.ioc)

### 🔧 Pin Configuration
- PA9 → USART1_TX
- PA10 → USART1_RX

### ⏱️ Clock Configuration
- HSI oscillator used
- Default system clock

### 🧩 Peripheral Configuration
- USART1 enabled
- Baud rate: 9600
- Mode: Asynchronous

